&lt;li&gt;Monitors weekly and monthly business performance, leads gap analysis, and drives corrective action plans to improve results against forecast and plan.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Builds and maintains customer-specific promotional, flyer, and display plans that support executional excellence and business objectives.&lt;/li&gt;
