&lt;li&gt;Partners proactively with internal and external stakeholders to align priorities, resolve issues, and advance business goals.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Shapes strategic business-building plans to capitalize on market opportunities, mitigate risk, and strengthen customer performance.&lt;/li&gt;
