&lt;p&gt;The Senior Manager, Marketing – Fragrance operates as the NA business owner within the US Brand Marketing team; with accountability for brand&lt;s&gt;s&lt;/s&gt; performance, marketing strategy development, budget management, and execution for the Juicy Couture Brand and all assigned Prestige Fragrance franchises. The role &lt;strong&gt;owns&lt;/strong&gt; key aspects of the business end-to-end and brings a clear strategic point of view to brand and portfolio decisions.&lt;/p&gt;
