&lt;li&gt;Establish governance frameworks that guide supplier onboarding, supplier performance management, risk evaluation, and decision rights across all business units.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Develop communication materials and reporting that clearly articulate Procurement’s value contribution to the Executive Team, brands, and all functional leaders.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Lead organizational change management and stakeholder engagement efforts that reinforce adoption of Center of Excellence practices and elevate Procurement

